                <note rend="inline" type="source">823.00/297: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Peru</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">McMillin</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-08-28T16:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 28, 1919, 4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>In view of the facts reported in your August 26th, 8 p.m., you are instructed to
                    address an informal communication to the Minister of Foreign Affairs of the
                    Leguia government informing him that the Government of the United States extends
                    to Mr. Leguia recognition as the head of the <hi rend="italic">de facto</hi>
                    Government of Peru.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
